I gotta say, this game seems really unpolished when compared to the dev‚Äôs other games. Especially that soft lock that happened in the mine cart section. That sound that played when she hit the button on the last door was a canned sound effect of the minecart carrying the fish and then crashing.

What they should have done was made that last button covered up by something until the mine cart reaches the last door, triggering the cover to fall off. That way the player won‚Äôt accidentally sequence break. If your levels are open like that, you need to account for the fact that players will do things in different orders.
